title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 12: Milt Schmidt, WJC, Blue Jackets & More
description:
On this week's ep, the boys discuss the legacy of Milt Schmidt, the incredible World Juniors tourney, and the hot-as-a-pistol Blue Jackets before tackling #AllRightHamilton and #AskAMillennial.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
